tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE digital_literacy_campaigns_performance (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(100),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    target_audience VARCHAR(100),
    budget DECIMAL,
    total_impact INT
);

CREATE TABLE digital_campaign_performance (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    campaign_start_date DATE,
    campaign_end_date DATE,
    total_participants INT,
    total_engagements INT
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_engagement_details (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    participant_id INT,
    engagement_type VARCHAR(50),
    engagement_date TIMESTAMP,
    engagement_duration INT,
    engagement_result VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT NOT NULL,
    metrics_type VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    metric_value INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE participant_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT NOT NULL,
    participant_id INT NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    submission_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE digital_literacy_campaigns (
  campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  total_participants INT
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(255),
  participant_age INT,
  participant_gender VARCHAR(10),
  campaign_id INT REFERENCES digital_literacy_campaigns(campaign_id)
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_activities (
  activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  activity_name VARCHAR(255),
  activity_date DATE,
  activity_duration INT,
  campaign_id INT REFERENCES digital_literacy_campaigns(campaign_id)
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT REFERENCES campaign_participants(participant_id),
  feedback_date DATE,
  feedback_description TEXT,
  campaign_id INT REFERENCES digital_literacy_campaigns(campaign_id)
);

CREATE TABLE digital_campaigns (
    campaign_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_metrics (
    metric_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID REFERENCES digital_campaigns(campaign_id),
    date_measured DATE,
    impressions INT,
    clicks INT,
    conversions INT
);

CREATE TABLE audience_demographics (
    demo_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID REFERENCES digital_campaigns(campaign_id),
    age_group TEXT,
    gender TEXT,
    location TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_influencers (
    influencer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID REFERENCES digital_campaigns(campaign_id),
    influencer_name TEXT,
    social_media_platform TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_feedback (
    feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID REFERENCES digital_campaigns(campaign_id),
    feedback TEXT,
    rating INT
);
